            <help_text>LoRaWAN速 is a global LPWAN specification created and maintained by the LoRa Alliance速 to drive a single standard for seamless interoperability&lt;br/&gt;
			across IoT markets. LoRaWAN is a medium access control (MAC) layer protocol but acts mainly as a network layer protocol for &lt;br/&gt;
			managing communications between LoRaWAN gateways and end-node devices.</help_text>
            <!-- Links that will be displayed on the help widgets:
            - filter: In case a selection needs to be made, use it as regexp on mcu name (STM32F042T6x)
            - display: string that will be displayed in front of the hyperlink
